etomica.atom.iterator

Class MoleculeIteratorArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.atom.iterator.MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
      • etomica.atom.iterator.MoleculeIteratorArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomsetIterator, MoleculeIterator, MoleculeIteratorMoleculeDependent, MoleculesetIterator, java.io.Serializable

    public class MoleculeIteratorArrayList
extends MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
implements MoleculeIteratorMoleculeDependent
    An atom iterator of the elements from an AtomArrayList (in proper sequence). Iterator will fail if element are added to or removed from list while iteration is proceeding.
